		<b>Comment By Jenny Shank, 1-19-08</b>
		<p>Speaking of literature of the urban west--I've been trying my hand at writing it.  My novel "Mile High," set in Denver, is a semi-finalist in this American-Idol type contest sponsored by Amazon.com, so now I am shamelessly trolling for people to review a chapter of it so I can advance in the competition.  If you're willing, check it out here (It's under my fiction writing name, J. Alicia Shank):<br />
<br />
